uildhall university now known as london metropolitan university on  december  he was awarded an honorary doctorate of business administration he joined colgatepalmolive in the united kingdom in  from  to  he served as executive vice president in  he was appointed chief operating officer with responsibility for operations in north america europe central europe asia and africa in  he became president and continued to serve as coo he was elected president chief executive officer and joined the board of directors in  in  he became chairman of the board of directors and continued on as president and ceo he has sat on the board of directors of pepsico since march   he is also a director of catalyst he sits on the board of directors of the consumer goods forum in  he earned over us million referencesedit  a b c d e f g h forbes  a b c d e f g h i j businessweek  a b c d e f g nndb  a b c d e f colgatepalmolive executive management team  a b c d e f g h pepsico board of directors and committees  a b colgate executive promoted spurring talk about top post the new york times july    catalyst board of directors  consumer goods forum website board of directors v t e colgatepalmolive people current ian m cook president chairman and ceo former william colgate founder john t cahill david foster ellen hancock martin ittner richard kogan george henry lesch delano lewis david j mahoney ed mcateer jan miner stephen sadove brands ajax baby magic bambeanos cibaca cold power colgate darlie fresh start hills pet nutrition irish spring kolynos lady speed stick mennen murphy oil soap palmolive sanex science diet skin bracer softsoap speed stick suavitel teen spirit toms of maine ultra brite vel soap related the colgate comedy hour colgate clock indiana colgate clock jersey city dr simon locke ftc v colgatepalmolive co united states v colgate  co category commons retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleianmcookoldid categories alumni of london guildhall universitybritish businesspeop